    • Constructor Detail

      • AdsbAirbornePositionMessage

        public AdsbAirbornePositionMessage(int type,
                           int df,
                           int ca,
                           java.lang.String payload,
                           java.lang.String icao,
                           java.lang.String timestamp)
        Save aircraft's information

        Constructor takes the parameters and decodes them further. Type, DFCA, ICAO and Timestamp are used by the superclasses' constructor, payload is evaluated to create and save data.

        Parameters:
        type - Messagetype, used to distinguish the Messages
        df - Downlink Format, contains information about data
        ca - CApability
        payload - contains data
        icao - International Civilian Aircraft Organization Airport Code
        timestamp - Time of receipt
